'''Embassies Row''' was an area of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Dometown (Coruscant)|Dometown]]. The main offices of the [[Senate Select Committee for Refugees]] were located there, along with the embassies of many [[Alien/Legends|non-human]] [[Species/Legends|species]].<ref name="NJO">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref>

